# ==============================================================================
# Multi-Target Speaker Extraction - .gitignore
# ==============================================================================

# 1. Audio Files Strategy | 音频文件策略
# Ignore all common audio formats by default (protects private data)
# 默认忽略所有音频格式（保护 .wav 等私有训练数据）
*.wav
*.mp3
*.ogg
*.m4a
*.aac
*.wma

# Exception: Allow FLAC files for sample audio
# 例外：允许提交 .flac 格式（用于示例音频）
!*.flac

# ==============================================================================
# Python & Environment | Python与环境
# ==============================================================================
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
.Python
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/
.installed.cfg
*.egg

# Virtual Environment | 虚拟环境
venv/
env/
.venv/

# ==============================================================================
# IDE / Editor | 编辑器配置
# ==============================================================================
.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
.DS_Store

# ==============================================================================
# Project Specific | 项目特定
# ==============================================================================
# Output directory: Ignore contents but keep folder structure
# 输出目录：忽略内容但保留文件夹结构
output/*
!output/.gitkeep

# Temporary files & Logs | 临时文件与日志
temp/
*.tmp
*.log
# Model checkpoints | 模型权重
*.nemo
*.ckpt
*.pt
*.pth
